      <textAnnotation id="sid-01F555F1-C9A1-428D-84D3-754F4F4662E6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process tower: OTC-Order To Cash
Process Group: O-Order Management
Process: O-020-100A Create Standard Order (IP)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0E11397B-376F-45E2-B1A7-DE2C74AB6055" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. MMID stands for Material ID and CPN stands for Customer Part Number
2. Not all customers have a CPN for every IP Product. 
3.Based on the MMID attributes system will recognize IRC relevant line items</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F176F356-BB71-4673-981F-35A147C3B957" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Price Changes due to Price Override will be considered during price calculation</text>
      </textAnnotation>
