      <textAnnotation id="sid-A8FF27CD-6D92-4C83-A5C1-80D90A8B2F56" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.CBA acquires, records and attaches all appropriate documents for justification.
2.Based on the item categories configured in S/4, IRC (Intel Registration Centre) process will be supported in the standard order flow</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-95DC553D-A87C-4B67-B0A6-16D47074A788" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.Based on the item categories configured in S/4, IRC (Intel Registration Centre) process will be supported in the standard order flow</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D4348D6A-9BED-4264-8057-5B25A1FC8CBB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.Both tangible and non-tangible products can take standard order process route</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-08E4BA90-97E6-4539-8D37-D115903C0E74" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
